Package: GUIDEseq
Type: Package
Title: GUIDE-seq and PEtag-seq analysis pipeline
Version: 1.32.0
Date: 2023-04-07
Encoding: UTF-8
Author: Lihua Julie Zhu, Michael Lawrence, Ankit Gupta,
       Hervé Pagès , Alper Kucukural, Manuel Garber, Scot A. Wolfe
